    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who systematically analyze, list, and describe items in a collection and arrange the information into a catalog, such as a person who performs descriptive cataloguing and subject analysis in a museum or library.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
